songs.title: Intro (Mastermind)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
What is this?
Maybach Music
I like this Maybach Music
(Sweet!)

[Brigde: Rick Ross]
"Push it to the-"
"Everyday I'm-"
"Ten years later-for me to cash out"
"Chickens put me in position"
"At the top"

[Interlude: Napoleon Hill]
Now there is something you need to know about the mastermind
In order to understand the overall concept and the prior to achieve success in all that you do
You must know that you can borrow other people knowledges, achievements, life experiences, and even their personal ressources in order to execute your own life goals
By adapting this one idea, you can achieve more in a short time than you could in a lifetime otherwise

[Brigde: Rick Ross]
“I stand boss and I mean that”

[Outro: Napoleon Hill]
We all know that you cannot get something for nothing
There is a price tag to everything
Even your own success
